I know that 99.9 percent of all NDEs are positive experiences. You  
have a few people who discuss hell-like situations but that is almost  
nil percent.

I&#39;m not really a big fan of mediums &quot;freeing&quot; trapped souls. I think  
it says more about the medium than the soul. That&#39;s my opinion and  
I&#39;ve had a lot of years in parapsychology to form it. I&#39;m not trying  
to ruffle anyone&#39;s feathers. I haven&#39;t been posting here a lot for a  
while, so you don&#39;t know me. Really, I am not ever disrespecting  
anyone&#39;s opinion, just disgreeing with it. :)


What you write about the Gettysburg hauntings is speculation that I  
agree with, but I still don&#39;t see any connection to the Fish Group  
and NDEs.

Ann

